{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/your_shops_your_rules.gif?t=1738090730\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>YOU ARE THE OWNER OF THAT FAMOUS GUN SHOP!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is now your kingdom! Whenever customers need a reliable gunsmith, you are their first stop. As they browse your shelves, they feel your unique touch in every corner of the shop, ready to make a name for itself in the city. Come on, turn your shop into the place of your dreams!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/2.gif?t=1738090730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WITH A MASTER'S TOUCH, GUNS COME TO LIFE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every weapon has a story, and it\u2019s up to you to continue it. Carefully examine incoming orders, identify the problems, and showcase your skills. Clean, repair, and renew the mechanisms! Step by step, you will be the one bringing these weapons back to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/3.gif?t=1738090730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>AS GOOD AS NEW: CLEAN AND READY!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether it's an old rifle or a modern handgun, every weapon deserves a second chance. First, clean the weapons, then skillfully repair them. Replace the parts and restore the broken mechanisms. Now, that weapon is ready to shine again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/4.gif?t=1738090730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THE FINAL TOUCH: POLYGON TEST!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every re